title: Week 9 NFL Preview & Bruce Feldman Chat
itunes:title: Week 9 NFL Preview & Bruce Feldman Chat
description:
DJ & Bucky preview all the matchups on the Week 9 NFL slate (1:17). Bruce Feldman of The Athletic & Fox Sports joins the show to discuss his article on Baker Mayfield vs. Patrick Mahomes 2016 thriller in Lubbock, plus they also discuss which college coaches may get a look at future NFL vacancies (17:50). The guys end the show with their college picks for Week 10, including the showdown in Baton Rouge between No. 1 Alabama vs. No. 3 LSU (39:40).
